<D>__{what are you talking about?}
<C>__{john tuld}
<D>__{this won't be the last `situation' i will be having this week. it's just the start.}
<C>__{sam rogers}
<D>__{it's only the start because we are starting it.}
<C>__{john tuld}
<D>__{maybe. but i don't think that's true, not this time. the numbers just don't add up anymore.}
<C>__{sam rogers}
<D>__{well i agree with you there, i've been saying that for years.}
